snippet.textDisplay:
I loved this song.

Edit:- No, I have no complaints.

Original:-
But I have a complaint. If something CS Pakistan has taught me, it is that you need to give English translation in subtitles to allow international audience to vibe with the song, like I would listen to Dari, Pashto songs and still know its meaning, despite the fact that I can't even read those languages. But what sense would this song make to an American or European who doesn't know Hindi?
